{"tid":331723,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"你地去旅行買套票定分開買","createTime":"2017-07-22T11:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T13:02:39.000Z","uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"09c6068bf8d5a56bffbc38bdc607b3871138603c","tid":331723,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T11:58:17.000Z","msg":"我通常都分開買<br />\n<br />\n機票<br />\n1.上Skyscanner睇下個價<br />\n2.去當地航空公司睇價<br />\n3.睇時間 （唔太重要 唔好深夜arrived就得）<br />\n4.買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n酒店<br />\n<a href=\"http://1.上booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.%E4%B8%8Abooking.com&d=0ZIkajYtF%2BW%2FKAAioOGknqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=6bfd548f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">1.上booking.com</a>睇價<br />\n2.睇環境<br />\n3.睇有冇得free cancellation (萬一睇到仲好可以隨時轉時間同其他酒店 不過一買左機票通常都唔郁)<br />\n4.睇評價<br />\n5.買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你地又點<br />\n分開買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n套票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e7e580860e089612c5fa343f10b8b985049defe","tid":331723,"uid":62719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:56:15.000Z","msg":"睇情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇到套票啲酒店唔啱自己 就會分開買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed122b520324a2770af7262209db20a39c08119","tid":331723,"uid":101961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T13:02:39.000Z","msg":"同樓主一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}